{"tid":2350002,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"許樹昌：考慮借調海關及入境署等紀律部隊協助採樣工作","createTime":"2021-01-02T03:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T08:28:03.000Z","uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8baae24d5f93af330314289a949c9ed7d39e59e9","tid":2350002,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T03:51:15.000Z","msg":"醫管局正研究分階段落實所有醫護人員定期接受檢測，中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌指，會考慮借調海關及入境署等紀律部隊協助採樣工作。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌：「檢測量已加大不少，如八千至一萬，一天之內要做到，但如果突然間很多幢大廈列入名單，住客太多，公私營合作很重要，一定要大家配合。現在不是單靠衞生署，而是要借調其他部門，例如入境處或海關，現時機場不忙碌，會否有人手借出來，上一些短的課程，教他們做採樣。」<br />\n<br />\nPK 點可以無警察？立左國安法無晒黑暴最得閒唔係佢地？"},{"pid":"42f9072d53667091b7e8db845e130106a02fae42","tid":2350002,"uid":211941,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T05:15:43.000Z","msg":"TMD Yellow C 不信任咱们香港公安吗？为啥不借调牠们？"},{"pid":"4125c1a326e40f179a1e707b6a2399d406cc150a","tid":2350002,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:07:21.000Z","msg":"[求推] 衞生署 強制檢測名單 又双叒叕有錯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2349363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2349363</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e035f1ac820e651d52ceae83746a16d298c391bd","tid":2350002,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:32:45.000Z","msg":"家下軍權制，點敢叫皇軍去做，緊係搵啲散仔去死先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06a8c0d5e9441b71758389b967dd7b36f675747","tid":2350002,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ePblb854PQYCcPIBm4A6q5lHvOE=/468x543/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NCJAYOZ4RGHIHBLROPAQF37OJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FePblb854PQYCcPIBm4A6q5lHvOE%3D%2F468x543%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledail